transfer
├── when amount is zero
│   └── it should revert
└── when amount is not zero
    ├── given sender has insufficient balance
    │   └── it should revert
    └── given sender has sufficient balance
        ├── when recipient is the sender
        │   └── it should succeed without transfer
        └── when recipient is different
            ├── it should transfer the amount
            ├── it should update balances
            └── it should emit a Transfer event
